description: Patricia O'Connor's body was found in nine locations in the Dublin mountains in June 2017.
title: Patricia O'Connor: Fourth person guilty over murder

maintext: It was found Louise O'Connor had agreed or acquiesced to her daughter, Stephanie, disguising herself as Patricia O'Connor to conceal the fact that she was already dead, knowing that Greene had murdered her.
